website top re: hp85b awakens by kaimaiguy on tue jul 19, 2011 1:50 am good moaning all!well many thanks for the flicker lead i have managed to upload a few pics of the machine but still trying to figure out how to make them accessable from here.i have managed to get a display so fears of a totally dead crt have abated however tis little more than so much goobly gooch with a steady stream of ps and # . probably a problem with the logic board or dips themselves i would imagine. there is no actual boot up the leds on the printer light up and the occasional display. there is also a dip missing in what i believe may be the memory bank on the logic board but not quite sure as i still have no board layout info and no schematic. i suppose also i expected to hear a fan upon power up but doesn't seem to exist here. prolly becuase the older cpus may not have been as hot so didnt require them again not sure.i actually recall seeing similar dips hanging on the component racks of radio shack back in the states years ago. would love to attempt a replacment but now that they are most likely considered museum display subjects themselves would most likely be hard to locate and a tad pricey at any rate.be well gentlemen and have the finest of dayscheers!rick kaimaiguy posts: 12joined: thu jul 07, 2011 6:03 pm top re: hp85b awakens by tezza on tue jul 19, 2011 12:54 pm hi rick,glad to see you got the video going. how did you do that? was it just a case of de-oxidising some connectors or a larger job?the missing dip may or may not be significant. sometimes sockets are included on machines for extra roms and the like. however, if you know its a socket for a memory chip and its the only one missing in a bank of them then that is suspicious. ram was often organized in banks corresponding to rows on the circuit board. unexpanded vintage machines might have a bank empty but seldom just one socket.apart from swapping chips and checking for broken connectors its quite hard to progress without a circuit diagram or a manual showing the mode of operation. did you try to hook up with some of those other hp85 users in some of the internet groups? im sure one of them will have some schematics scanned.one fairly generic thing you can do is to check the cpu with a multimeter to see if its working. (power, clock, reset line etc.). however the machine does have a proprietary cpu so finding just what pin does what might be a problem. if it was a z80 or 6502 it would be a lot easier.to my knowledge the hp85 units never had a fan. the processor is actually quite slow and it probably doesnt get hot enough to warrant one. tez (terry stewart) (administrator)collection: ... /index.htmprojects and articles: @classiccomputnz | youtube: terry stewarttrade me: tezza5 tezza site admin posts: 2311joined: thu jan 01, 1970 12:00 pmlocation: palmerston north, new zealand website top re: hp85b awakens by lizardb0y on tue jul 19, 2011 1:02 pm hi rick, i don't have a schematic but i can take a high resolution photo of my hp85 board this weekend if that well help. it should let you identify what chips go where at least lizardb0y / andrewjust another 8-bit hustlerblog: @vintage8bitgoogle+: andrew9 - over 500 positive trades. lizardb0y posts: 549joined: mon oct 06, 2008 8:50 amlocation: wellington website top re: hp85b awakens by tezza on tue jul 19, 2011 1:20 pm rick,in looking around the web i found a repair manual here: actually a detailed "training guide" for technicians, and it has the theory of operation and circuit diagrams etc. should be useful!the site has quite a few user manuals too. have a look. luck! tez (terry stewart) (administrator)collection: ... /index.htmprojects and articles: @classiccomputnz | youtube: terry stewarttrade me: tezza5 tezza site admin posts: 2311joined: thu jan 01, 1970 12:00 pmlocation: palmerston north, new zealand website top re: hp85b awakens by kaimaiguy on tue jul 19, 2011 1:59 pm dear sirs n ladies n germsi am so grateful for your kind input and for all the time you have taken to respond to my posts. as i said before i lack the lot tools, resources and know how. so when you suggest that i use a multimetter to check the whatsis on the cpu it's very vague to me.so far what i detect is a ticking sound which seems to be originating down in the right center of the power supply. this is s steady beat tick tick tick then sometimes it's not there at all. the diplsay is not steady either and only appears on occasional basis.the interior is very clean and i see little in the way of corrosion but probably doesn't rule out a good clean. just hoping to be able to get downtown sometime to get some alcohol hopefully.also unfortunately my own internet machine is riddled with problems i have a very slow rural dial up connection with kiwionline which makes surfing truly a miserable experience can't use utube etc just too slow. can't find this page can;t find explorer and can't even access my email half the time. my isp knows nothing.aside from the one chip missing all else seems to be there on the logic board and so far there are no apparent visable signs of any problem areas. this is why my thoughts remain with probable bad logic etc.thank you for the url to the tech manual i already downloaded it and many others that is why i felt ok about starting out on the project clear concise and proper disassembly instructions. ian emailed me and suggested that the machine may still be trying to access the other box it was connected to while in it's former use and that i might try to connect the interface that came along with it. so i guess nothing tried nothing gained. if this starts getting into a money thing i will simply have to ditch the project. i just don't like seeing a thing of beauty sleeping like this when it can be wide awake and enjoying it's continuing cyber life.again i thank you all for everythinghave the finest of days.cheers!rick kaimaiguy posts: 12joined: thu jul 07, 2011 6:03 pm top re: hp85b awakens by tezza on tue jul 19, 2011 2:08 pm kaimaiguy wrote:the interior is very clean and i see little in the way of corrosion but probably doesn't rule out a good clean. just hoping to be able to get downtown sometime to get some alcohol hopefully.is this to clean the corrosion or for medicinal purposes when you come to a blind alley in the diagnosis? i'm glad you have that manual. a ticking sound in the psu is not a good sign. in fact i would start there. make sure the right voltage is coming off the psu (be careful where you probe). it's best tested with the motherboard plugged in so it has some load. if the voltages being supplied to the board and vdu aren't correct and steady then this will cause a whole host of problems including all of the ones you describe.p.s. be very careful measuring around the vdu. there is high voltage around those things. hopefully that manual will suggest where to measure to check that you're getting correct power levels. tez (terry stewart) (administrator)collection: ... /index.htmprojects and articles: @classiccomputnz | youtube: terry stewarttrade me: tezza5 tezza site admin posts: 2311joined: thu jan 01, 1970 12:00 pmlocation: palmerston north, new zealand website top re: hp85b awakens by kaimaiguy on tue jul 19, 2011 3:06 pm hi thank you very much for your postas i said before i have no clue as to how to do many of these operations. not sure where to put the probes etc and exactly what i am looking for. what do you mean by " the right voltage" what is the right voltage are we talking mains voltage , board voltage etc etc? also you say that the ticking is not a good sign what could some of the causes be?the alcohol was suggested by another older member here to clean up the boards, circuits etc. again however there is really no signs of visable corrosion.thanks for allrick kaimaiguy posts: 12joined: thu jul 07, 2011 6:03 pm top re: hp85b awakens by zl2aox on tue jul 19, 2011 3:53 pm the ticking sounds like high-voltage arcing due to insulation breakdown. if a damaged or discoloured component isn't apparent, it might be easier to spot in darkness. however, i'd strongly reiterate tezza's cautions - be very careful what you touch! zl2aox posts: 74joined: sun sep 12, 2010 12:30 pmlocation: palmerston north top re: hp85b awakens by tezza on tue jul 19, 2011 8:08 pm kaimaiguy wrote:as i said before i have no clue as to how to do many of these operations. not sure where to put the probes etc and exactly what i am looking for. what do you mean by " the right voltage" what is the right voltage are we talking mains voltage , board voltage etc etc? your manual should help with this. normally 240v goes into the psu and dc voltage goes out to the mainboard. just what this is and just how many dc lines there are depends on the computer. there is amost always a 5v one and often there is a 12v one and a -5v one also (on a computer as old as yours). however, it's possible some of those voltages could be generated on the board itself. anyway these dc voltages should be at the levels stated in the manual and stready. check the manual and see where these lines connect to the mainboard. measure them where the connect or close to where they connect, but before they go through any components. there are lots of other places you could also measure the voltages but you'd have to use the schematic to find them. i'm assuming you know how to use a multimeter?i agree with zl2aox that it sounds like your psu is shorting. it certainly shouldn't be ticking. it's possible that a capacitor has shorted perhaps or (more seriously) the insulation. if the voltages are out of wack on the board, that would confirm it.your psu would also have a (high voltage) lead to the screen. unless you really know what you are doing it would be prudent to stay way from this. there are high (lethal) voltages in that area, and the power doesn't even need to be on. i would advise strongly not to go near it with a probe (or anything) until you are a lot more skilled. in fact, a psu (especially a shorting one) can also be dangerous to novices so i would advise not poking around the psu as well.given the risk factor here, consider that this might be just a bridge too far. i was at about your level when i started tinkering around with these machines but i started on a really well known and well documented machine (apple ii+), had duplicate machines, and the issues were neither psu or screen. i also had an electronics mate (philip avery) to explain and assist from time to time. it took me a while to build up expertise before i would go near a screen or psu. even now they still make me nervous. tez (terry stewart) (administrator)collection: ... /index.htmprojects and articles: @classiccomputnz | youtube: terry stewarttrade me: tezza5 tezza site admin posts: 2311joined: thu jan 01, 1970 12:00 pmlocation: palmerston north, new zealand website top re: hp85b awakens by kaimaiguy on wed jul 20, 2011 10:00 pm good evening mateswell i believe i have found at least one of the major ailments located on the logicthere is a battery of of 3 silver cylinder caps which are c1 c2 and c3. two of these caps are blown out on one end the positve end of c1 and the negative end of ajoining c2. the leads appear to have been fried being a dark brown colour. these caps i believe supply/regulate the voltage to the crt ribbon cables which connect the logic pca to the large crt pca. this is also the exact area where i believe i heard the ticking sound.still looking for further dead soldiers which i expect to find but very hopefully do not. the very next hopeful thing is to be able to find replacements or suitable subs. i also believe that u21 pm021 (the missing dip) may have been essential rom to the machine thus another finger missing from the hand. this i am however unsure of as to whether or not this chip is essential to drive the neccessary logic to make the machine operational.will keep all posted on progressi thank you all again for your help and kind support during this first of my sojurns into bringing another ole timer back to the world of the living.cheers!rick kaimaiguy posts: 12joined: thu jul 07, 2011 6:03 pm top re: hp85b awakens by tezza on wed jul 20, 2011 2015 calendar abril 2018 l m x j v s d  mar 1 2345678 9101112131415 16171819202122 23242526272829 30 shaun white, el dios extremo dic 23, 2013 by consuelo cuesta in deportes rate this post shaun white. para quien no lo conozca todava es un dios de los deportes extremos. snowboard, surf, skate este chico ha nacido con una tabla en los pies. hablar de los xgames, es hablar de shaun white. su apellido no puede ir ms acorde a su profesin. es como el john nieve de juego de tronos, el mejor en lo suyo. esta tabla habla por si sola. con tan solo 27 aos lo ha ganado todo. medallas de shaun white evento premio ao x games medal record medalla de oro 2012 olympic mens snowboarding medalla de oro 2010 olympic mens snowboarding medalla de oro 2006 x games medal record medalla de plata 2002 x games medal record medalla de plata 2002 x games medal record medalla de oro 2003 x games medal record medalla de oro 2004 x games medal record medalla de oro 2005 x games medal record medalla de oro 2006 x games medal record medalla de oro 2006 x games medal record medalla de plata 2007 x games medal record medalla de bronce 2006 x games medal record medalla de plata 2005 x games medal record medalla de oro 2007 ttr world snowboard tour record medalla de plata 2007 x games medal record medalla de plata 2010 x games medal record medalla de oro 2011 la carrera de shaun white comenzaba con 9 aos con otro grande, tony hawk. se conocieron en un skatepark local y comenz a ser su mentor para introducirle en el mundo del skate. con 17 aos, shaun white, ya competa a nivel profesional y lograba varios ttulos. el ms importante de ellos en el action sports tour champion. no solamente domina la tabla del skate, en snowboard tambin es un dios de los deportes extremos. esta pasin por los deportes extremos viene de su hermano mayor. con siete aos ya tena un sponsor como rider en la disciplina del snow. shaun white, el dios de los deportes extremos amplia experiencia de shaun white durante su carrera particip en dos juegos olmpicos de invierno. en los juegos olmpicos de invierno del 2006 y 2010, gan la medalla de oro en el evento de snowboard halfpipe. tambin particip en los x games de invierno, donde gan medallas desde 2002. incluyendo todos las competencias de los x games de invierno a travs del 2009, sus medallas son 15 (10 de oro, 3 de plata y 2 de bronce). no queda ninguna duda de que es el dios de los deportes extremos. el deportista total. hace lo que le gusta y vive de ello. sin duda, un chico con suerte. esperemos que este rider nos siga dando alegras y disfrutemos con sus trucos imposibles. __label__low toggle navigation home tve tipy test workshopy konzultace galerie nabzme e-book pohyb a redukce hmotnosti v e-booku naleznete odpovdi na otzky pro se hbat, jakou pohybovou aktivitu zvolit, abyste mli anci u n vydret, jak intenzita pohybu je vhodn k redukci hmotnosti, co jst ped a po cvien a na co je pi cvien nutn rozhodn pamatovat. e - booky ekaj na vs vymazlen e-booky zdarma i za symbolick penz. kad kniha se vnuje nktermu z velkch tmat zdravho ivotnho stylu  fit jdelnku vetn recept a postupu ppravy, pohybu i motivaci, hubnut, prevenci nemoc, cvien na bolav zda, pevn bicho a mrncovn pozad. video - posilovn bicha tak jak? zvldnete pln poet opakovan posilovn binho svalstva jako my s terezou a brou? pokud nezvldnete hned pln poet opakovn posilovacch cvik, vbec nevad. postupn si poty opakovn pidvejte. pi posilovn, nejenom binch sval, nezadrujte dech, nekmitejte, nevihejte. bedra jsou vdy plnou plochou pitisknut k podloce. bolesti zad, kdy je teba vyhledat odbornka? civilizan onemocnn - bolesti zad bolesti zad pat mezi tzv. civilizan onemocnn. alespo jednou v ivot se s nm setkalo 80% dosplch lid. kdy zvldnu bolesti zad sm? piny bolest zad mou bt rzn. jak rozlime, kdy si s bolestmi jet meme poradit sami a kdy bychom u mli vyhledat odbornou pomoc?jednm z indiktor, jak rozliit druh bolesti je innost, pi kterch ns zda bol.mte-li obte pi dlouhm a neergonomickm sezen, pravdpodobn se jedn pouze o bolesti zad v dsledku nevhodn statick zte a pome vm zmna nastaven pracovnho prosted a zven vai denn pohybov aktivity. jestlie vs bol zda pi dlouhm stn, mete patit mezi jedince, kte maj tzv. vadn dren tla a u v dsledku anatomickch pomr (nastaven jednotlivch ptench segment, ppadn pnve vi sob) nebo v dsledku svalov nerovnovhy. i tato pina se d do jist mry eit vhodnou pohybovou aktivitou a zmnou pracovn zte. stres a bolesti zad dalm z vznamnch faktor ovlivujc bolesti zad je stres. nkdy me bt stres samotnou pinou, jindy me bt spoutcm faktorem do t doby spcho problmu. vznamnou roli ve vzniku bolest ptee hraje obezita, ale tak nevhodn fyzick zt (nadmrn, jednostrann,). mte-li bolesti zad nebo i jinch st pohybovho apartu pi uritm sportu, je to znmka toho, e nco dlte patn. nkdy pome jedna konzultace s fyzioterapeutem, kter pinu odhal a doporu, jak ji odstranit. kdy vyhledat odbornou pomoc pro bolesti zad? kdy bychom mli zpozornit a vyhledat odbornou pomoc? jestlie vm bolest propaguje do dolnch konetin, tsel nebo bicha, me jt o funkn nebo i strukturln poruchu ptee, se kterou si u neporadte sami a je vhodn vyhledat odbornou pomoc (fyzioterapeuta, rehabilitanho lkae, neurologa). fyzioterapeut vm po vyeten pohybovho apartu v souvislosti s va anamnzou stanov pinu obt, kterou vm pome vyeit nebo vs odele k dalmu nutnmu vyeten k odbornmu lkai.dalm z indiktor bolest zad, kdybychom mli vyhledat odbornou pomoc, jsou non bolesti, ostr bolest v reakci na kchnut nebo nemonost najt levovou polohu. nkdy mou bt bolesti zad prvn znmkou njakho internho onemocnn, kdy dochz k jeho manifestaci v rmci tzv. vertebroviscerlnch vztah (kad orgn se projevuje specifickm obrazem funknch poruch na pohybovm apartu). i s tmto si zkuen fyzioterapeut doke poradit, ppadn vs odeslat k dalmu odbornkovi. mgr. lenka hellebrandov fyzioterapie u vs doma hledte odbornka, fyzioterapeuta? vte, e mete mt odbornou fyzioterapeutickou i ergoterapeutickou pomoc pmo v pohodl domova? lenka advisory boardu pro fit institutu, autorka naich lnk na fyzioterapuetick a ergonomick tmata, vetn tohoto, mgr. lenka hellebrandov s kolegy od kvtna 2015 otevela ambulantn rehabilitan zazen hometherapy. ambulance jsou na praze 6 v ulici kladensk 41/241, 50m od metra boislavka. krom ambulantnch slueb, poskytuj tak fyzioterapii, ergoterapii a logopedii pmo v pohodl vaeho domova na zem prahy, brna, berouna, hoovic a kladna, a to v plnm komfortu a kvalit, jako v ambulantnch zdravotnickch zazench.objednat se mete na tel.: 774186189. potebujete filtr pro lnky, videa a e-booky? lnekvideoebook e - learningke staentipy pro jdlotipy pro motivacitipy pro pohybtipy pro prevenciworkshopy zobrazovat peten lnky sed, sedm, vichni sedme jak snit negativn dopady sedavho zamstnn? vtina populace m nzkou pohybovou aktivitu. pi sedavm zamstnn je nutn nejen pravideln sportovat, ale tak bhem dne zvit pohybovou aktivitu v rmci adl (activity of daily living  aktivity dennch innost)-chze do schod msto vtah, vystoupit o zastvku dv, apod. trochu pohybu na pracoviti neukod zmny polohy mezi sedem a stojem bhem pracovnho dne ulev napt v zdech, zlep posturu a dchn a pome celkovmu wellbeing.kdo idli m bydl, kdo stl, ten pracuje - ergonomie prce u pc hlava se v bnm ivot nastavuje tak, abychom mohli sledovat dn kolem sebe. a nejen to: u s pohybem o, nato pak s pohybem hlavy, se pipravuj vechny svaly na tle. s nastavenm hlavy je reflexn spojen aktivita veker muskulatury tla. pi pohledu vzhru a zklonu hlavy zanou automaticky aktivovat nebo i prohbat bedra (a pulit pozad). tak klon hlavy aktivuje vce svalstvo na stran klonu.fyzioterapie - svalov peten, pohybov stereotypy to, jak vstaneme ze idle, kolik udlme krok, a jakm zpsobem zvedneme horn konetinu k vypnai svtla, jak pracuje u potae s my, jsou procesy, kter se dj zcela mimovoln, bez naeho soustedn na jednotliv kony. asto se stv, e pi bnch dennch innostech nkter svaly pouvme nadmrn a jin svaly z funkce vynechvme a jakoby opomjme. tm pak dochz k chronickmu petovn uritch oblast, je me mt za nsledek i strukturln zmny.fit test  test ivotnho stylu test je sestaven na zklad tzv. evidence based medicine (medicny zaloen na dkazech) pomoc upravench dotaznk uznvanch odbornmi spolenostmi. mapuje rove pohybov aktivity, jdelnek, odolnost vi stresu, zt pohybovho apartu a rizika civilizanch onemocnn. ke kad oblasti ivotnho stylu vm dle vsledk fit testu udl pro fit znmku (1- nejlep, optimln stav a 5  nejhor, vysok riziko). ke kad znmce je navc doplnn podrobnj koment a osvden tipy, co by vm v dan oblasti mohlo pomoci.jak vznikaj patn pohybov stereotypy, poruchy pohybu poruchy pohybu mohou mt pvod nejen ve strukturln patologii, ale u ve zmnch nebo selhn podmnek pro realizaci pohybu. z klick praxe vyplv, e porucha funkce bv asto pinou bolest a jestlie trv dle, zpsobuje prokazateln morfologick zmny. na druh stran kad morfologick porucha vyvol cetrln odpov a vznik soubor funknch zmn, kter meme identifikovat a terapeuticky ovlivnit.posilovn binch sval a hlubok stabilizan systm ptee brnice a pnevn dno tak tvo dva jaksi psty, kter psob proti sob shora a zdola, m roztlauj polt orgn bin dutiny do zbylch smr - vped a do stran, resp. vzad. zde se uplatuje funkce pnho binho svalu, kter se aktivuje excentricky a brzd pohyb obsahu bin dutiny vped a do stran - pi ndechu se proto zvtuje obvod pasu.technika sprvnho brninho dchn pi cvien tento zpsob dchn je zkladem vech dalch cvik, protoe dochz prostednictvm aktivity binch sval a pnevnho dna k aktivaci nitrobinho tlaku, co je nutn pro sprvnou stabilizace ptee.svaly, tuky, kosti, vodavyeten tlesnho sloen chcete hubnout? dlte vechno sprvn, jdelnek skvl, pohybu dost a dost kad den, a peci se na vze nic nedje? nezoufejte, ve me bt na dobr cest. mnohdy na zatku hubnut sice ubv tuk, ale pokud jste navili pohybovou aktivitu, zane tak pibvat douc svalov hmota - "kilo za kilo", take na "vze" se zdnliv nemus nic dt. zda optimln hubnete, zjistte nejspolehlivji kontrolou tlesnho sloen.workshop - ve o pohybu workshop o keckch, tepovkch, minutch, svalech, pevnm bku a mrncovnm pozad. dozvte se, kolik je teba pohybu k redukci hmotnosti a kolik ke zlepen zdravotn prognzy. jakou volit efektivn pohybovou aktivitu prv pro vs. naute se hlavn zsady rozumnho posilovn a tolik potebnho protaen. poskytneme vm nvod k sestaven individulnho pohybovho plnu ke zlepen fyzick kondice i k redukci hmotnosti.pentov smoothie um oloupat bann, otevt krabici mlka a oloupat mandarinku? tak to zvldne tuhle bjenou svainku. a budete mon pekvapen, e pent me v kombinaci s ovocem takto chutnat.kdy me pohyb kodit naemu srdci? smyslem mho lnku nen odrazovn od pohybu a zastraovn, nbr nauknout, kdy mohou srden rizika hrozit. pzniv inky pravidelnho pohybu v mnoha ohledech pevyuj efekt lk. pohyb nm dl dobe od hlavy k pat, a u se jedn o prevenci deprese, zlepen kognitivnch schopnost (tj. lpe nm to pl) zlepen srden-cvnho apartu, prevenci cukrovky, kter ns svm vskytem vlcuje, jak nikdy ped tm. mme m dle vce podklad, e pravideln fyzick aktivity tak vznamn ovlivuje vskyt ndor. osoby, kter pravideln sportuj, se v prmru dovaj o 7 let vce ne jejich vrstevnci se sedavm zpsobem ivota.jak pedchzet zavacm obtm pi vytrvalostnm vkonu zsadn role zavacho traktu pi sportovnm vkonu tkv v dodvce tekutin a ivin. gastrointestinln (gi) neboli zavac obte v pln i dle statistik postihuj 30-90% vytrvalostnch bc. studie mezi vytrvalostnmi triatlety udv dokonce vskyt gastrointestinlnch obt u 93% zvodnk. gi obte jsou patrn nejastjm dvodem zhorenho vkonu pi vytrvalostnch zvodech a ovlivuj nsledn i regeneraci.jahodov smoothie s mandarinkou jednoduch sndan, svainka nebo prost nco dobrho na zub. dky tvarohu i jogurtu, tj. obsahu blkovin, m smoothie dobr sytc efekt.okurkov smoothie jako sndan i svaina zcela jednoduch npoj, kter zvldne pln kad, kdo m doma mixr, me poslouit jako sndan i skvl svainka.jak pedejt syndromu petrnovn i kdy nejsou jednoznan frekvence si mete vypotat dle rznch vzorc. pesnj je vak uren svho maxima pmo v ternu.plavu si a vm jak! jak si urit maximln tepovou frekvenci pi plavn pi rznm druhu sportu dosahujeme rzn maximln tepov frekvence  mtf. nejni tepov frekvence z ptice svatch aerobnch sport - chze, bh, jzda na kolem, bh na lych a plavn  dosahujeme prv pi plavn. hrub eeno pi plavn doshneme asi o 10-15% ni maximln tepov frekvence ne pi bhu.udren nebo rozvoj? kolik a jak asto cviit? vodem je poteba ci, e opravdu kad krok a kad kilogram se pot! nicmn, kdo cvi vce a dle na prvoplatn nrok na vt uitek a zdravotn benefit ze cvien. pohybov aktivity meme dle efektu rozdlit do 3 skupin: 1. udrujc pohybov aktivita  tj. setrvvm, udruji se v aktulnm danm stavu. i udren je nkdy velmi nron a je to malm i vtm vtzstvm.co jst ped a po cvien strava ped cvienm a po cvien vznamn ovlivuje nejen samotn cviebn vkon, ale i to, zda ns teba po cvien budou bolet svaly. pojte se podvat, jak by to mlo ped a po cvien optimln vypadat. bavme se o rozumnm rekreanm sportovn, s 2-3 trninkovmi jednotkami tdn. kdy pedpokldme, e cviebn jednotka trv kolem 60ti minut. nechce dramaticky pibrat svalovou hmotu, rsovat , ani neutome na sv osobn rekordy.jsou vae pedsevzet smart? chytr cl dvte si pedsevzet, teba ta novoron? pokud "ano" zkuste jej podrobit krtk analze. asto pouvan pomcka je anglick zkratka smart. pokud budou vae pedsevzet splovat parametry smart - chytrho cle maj velkou anci na spch.intenzita pohybov aktivity a redukce hmotnosti intenzita zte vyjden tepovou frekvenc rozhoduje o tom, jak efekt bude pohybov aktivita mt. chcete pohybem hlavn hubnout? nen nutn se zniit, zplavit, lapat po dechu. optimln rozmez pro redukci hmotnosti, tj. proto, aby tlo erpalo jako zdroj energie tukov zsoby, je intenzita pohybu v rozmez srden frekvence 60-75% va maximln tepov frekvence (mtf). nicmn nen to zas tak jednoduch, nkte autoi se piklnj k nim slm na 50-60% mtf, jin na druhou stranu preferuj spe submaximln hodnoty.stopa! jak si urit maximln tepovou frekvenci pi bhu na lych? hodnota maximln tepov frekvence - mtf zle na druhu sportu, kter provozujete. jin mtf doshnete pi bhu a nap. vznamn ni mtf doshnete pi plavn. uren mtf je vtinou nejpesnj pmo v ternu pi tom konkrtnm druhu sportu. jeliko lnek pi druh zimn den, je nasnad vysvtlit, jak si urte svou maximln tepovou frekvence pi bhu na lych.natankujte dve, ne vm zane svtit kontrolka, aneb jak na motivaci? motivace je jako benzin, kter lijeme do motoru na pevn vle. pevn vle nesta, kdy nen benzin, kter by ji pohnl. pojme tedy nahldnout, jak lze i svpomoc s motivac pracovat tak, abychom si vas natankovali. v prvn ad je teba si ujasnit, co vlastn chcete. vte to?abyste nebyla 10.- prevence ndoru prsu diagnozu ndoru prsu bohuel v esk republice usly kad 10. ena. vskyt tohoto onemocnn se posouv ke stle nim vkovm ronkm. mamografick vyeten nejinnj a nejefektivnj metodou zjitn rakoviny prsu v ranm stdiu.protaen nad zlato, postizometrick relaxace skoro vichni mme njakou tu svalovou skupinu zkrcenou, petenou a naopak protilehlou skupinu povolenou, "vyvalenou". kad mme urit pohybov stereotypy, tj. odrme se z jedn nohy, nkupy, dti a zbytek rodiny nosme na jednom boku, chzi po schodech zanme vdy stejnou nohou.magickch 10 000 - denn mnostv krok ijeme nejdel obdob bez vlek, hladomoru, epidemi smrtelnch infeknch nemoc mme se tu v echch a potamo v evrop vlastn skvle. chyb nm vbec nco? chyba bohuel stle vce a vce.prevence je vdy jednodu, mn nkladn, mn nron, mn bol ne lba vte na kter preventivn prohldky a v jakch intervalech mte nrok ze svho zdravotnho pojitn?kouen dv srdci pokouit cvy jsou tabkovm kouem pokozovny u pi mal expozici  sta tedy vykouit jen pr cigaret denn. dokonce sta i pobyt v zakouenm prosted. dopady se projev brzy, ale zrove riziko rychle kles  u druh den pot, co pestanete kouit, se riziko infarktu sniuje o tetinu. to plat i o pasivnm kouen.workshop - srden zleitost ston nkdo va rodin se srdkem? m v pokrevn pbuzn vysok krevn tlak, prodlal nkdo u vs v rodin infarkt? pokud ano, jste v riziku srdenho onemocnn. na workshopu zjistte, nakolik jste onemocnnm srdce konkrtn ohroeni. srozumiteln si vysvtlme, co pesn mete pro sv srdce udlat vy sami, co to je prevence srdench nemocnn, kdy a kter lkask prohldky byste mli absolvovat.stres je pes  jak ho vycviit? jak zvldat stres? hmm, to je sice blb, ale pedstav si co j , tak u jste nco podobnho od kamardky i ptele slyeli, pot, co jste jim vylili sv problmy? a ona i on msto toho, aby empaticky vyjdil, e v problm je opravdu zvan, ho mahem sfoukli ze stolu, s tm, e ten jejich problm je jet hor? vnmn stresu a problm je subjektivn. co pro jednoho znamen mravenit, me pro druhho znamenat mount everest. stres na ns v dnen dob h kdekoliv a je jedno, zda jste vrcholov manager nebo ena v domcnosti. stresu nezabrnme, pouze ho meme zvldnout.tak za kolik? jak mit obvod pasu? obvod pasu mme ve stoje, do pl tla vysvleeni, na holm tle. pas mme v polovin vzdlenosti mez horn hranou lopaty kosti kyeln a poslednm (spodnm) ebrem. nenechte se zmst pupkem, kter obas me bt u lid s krtkm trupem ne.rozchote to! jak navit denn mnostv pohybu? kad z ns je individuln, v jin fyzick kondici, s jinmi pohybovmi pedpoklady, s jinmi riziky, ale pro vechny plat, e pokud zvme pohybovou aktivitu o 30% nad souasn mnostv, pekrome tm prh, kter je nutn k dosaen efektu. toto 30% zven se pzniv projev na na zdravotn prognze.bojte se zubae? chodte k nmu pravideln! dospl maj nrok na preventivn prohldku u stomatologa jednou ron s tm, e zubn prevence je provdna i u oeten a vyeten registrovanho pacienta jednou za 1/2 roku. co zkontroluje zuba pi preventivn prohldce?odpovejte aneb jak na work-life balance e je na tma odpoinek. odpovat se m, to v pece kad. je dobr spt dostaten, to tak vichni vd. nem se nosit prce dom a jet mn na dovolenou. je dobr mt svho konka, pi kterm odpovte. je douc si ut as jen pro sebe. a dte se tm? dokete si udret tzv. work-life balance a ctit se u toho dobe?co mete ekat od fyzioterapie? co je fyzioterapeutick vyeten? fyzioterapie je jednou ze sloek lebn rehabilitace a jako samostatn metodicko-terapeutick obor se uplatuje ve vech oblastech medicny. fyzioterapie je lebnou metodou vyuvajc rznch forem energi k ovlivnn patologickch stav organismu. zabv se zejmna pohybovm systmem, ale tak monost ovlivnit pes pohybov systm poruchy dalch orgn.sladk nebezpe - diabetes mellitus diabetes mellitus neboli cukrovka je chronick onemocnn, pi kterm n organismus nen schopen udret hladinu krevnho cukru v normlnm rozmez (3,5-6,0mmol/l). podle toho, jak je dvod tto poruchy, rozliujeme cukrovku na vcero typ. nejastji se vyskytujc je cukrovka 2. typu, kterou dle poslednch daj trp v esk republice tm 900 000 pacient.mezi nmi dvaty - gynekologick prevence na preventivn gynekologickou prohldku m nrok kad dvka pi ukonen povinn koln dochzky a od 15 let pak jednou ron. soust preventivnho gynekologickho vyeten je zjitn osobnch i rodinnch daj a vlastn vyeten s pihldnutm k vku a zdravotnmu stavu.pro chcete jst? existuje mnoho lnk na tma jak jst a co jst. mlokdo si vak polo otzku pro. pokud se vzpamatujete z vodnho pekvapen, jak nkdo me vbec podobnou otzku vyslovit, zjistte mon spousty zajmavch vc, jakmile se na ni budete snait odpovdt. zkusme si zmnit ti nejastj odpovdi.praktick prevence od 18ti let mte jednou za dva roky nrok na preventivn prohldku u svho praktickho lkae. vte, co ve m obsahovat preventivn prohldka u praktickho lkae?voda je zklad, jak na pitn reim? chcete bt chytej, ilej, mn unaven, nemt bolesti hlavy a mt dobrou nladu, bt krsnj, s mn vrskami... to ve je ovlivnno pitnm reimem. kdy je n pitn reim nedostaten, krev je hust, plyne pomaleji, bude he okysliovat clov orgny, teba mozek, co vyst v podrdnost, hor koncentraci, navu.ano, chci bt fit, ale nemm na to as! mme pro vs dobrou i patnou zprvu. nejprve tu patnou  as se nad nathnout  den bude mt vdy pouze 24 hodin. ned se ani pikoupit ani naetit do zsoby ani vykouzlit zzranm proutkem. ta dobr je, e as b pro vechny stejnou rychlost a je na kadm z ns, jakm zpsobem s touto luxusn komoditou hospodame.kdy je poteba napnout vechny sly- prediabetes prediabetes je pozvolna se vyvjejc pechod mezi metabolickm syndromem a rozvojem cukrovky 2. typu. ve fzi prediabetu nen organismus schopn udret optimln rozmez hladiny krevnho cukru, ale jet nejsou dosaeny patologick hodnoty, kter by splovaly diagnzu cukrovky 2. typu. stanoven diagnzy prediabetu je velmi zsadn, je to obdob, kdy je mon rozvoji cukrovky 2. typu pedejt.kad 3. ech, kad 5.eka ho m...metabolick syndrom metabolick syndrom je kumulace rizikovch faktor srden cvnch onemocnn. pokud je vm diagnza metabolickho syndromu piknuta, vzte, e vae riziko mrt na srden-cvn onemocnn se zvyuje 3.6x. v echch se metabolick syndrom se vyskytuje u 32,5% mu a 21,4% en.nen cholesterol jako cholesterol hladiny krevnch tuk jsou vznamnm rizikovm faktorem srden-cvnch onemocnn, cukrovky a dalch nemoc. nrok na vyeten cholesterolu a jeho jednotlivch frakc v rmci preventivnho vyeten u svho praktickho lkae mte v 18, 40, 50 a 60 letech, nkter pojiovny hrad vyeten i ve 30ti letech.co vm nikdo neodpe? onemocnn srden cvnho apartu vznik nejastji na podklad aterosklerzy. aterosklerza je dlouhodob, mnoho let trvajc proces, kter zan v naich tepnch ji v dtstv. pedstavte si jak, z hladk, prun tepny se irokm prsvitem se stv rigidn, zen, tuh trubice, kter je nchyln k ucpn krevn sraeninou a k prasknut. tyto nedouc zmny mohou vystit v infarkt myokardu nebo mozkovou phodu. u kadho jedince je rychlost postupu aterosklerotickch zmn individuln a je ovlivnna ptomnost rizikovch faktor. rizikovch faktor je nkolik destek, ale ty zsadn, kter nai zdravotn prognzu nejvce ovlivn, meme spotat na prstech obou rukou.kolik a jak asto je potebn fyzick aktivita pro n zdravotn benefit vsledky jedn z nejvtch studi na tma fyzick aktivity, kter byla provedena na tvrt milionu osobch (leitzmann et al. 2007) potvrzuje, e opravdu kad krok a kad minuta strven fyzickou aktivitou je pro na zdravotn prognzu prospn. ve studii byli astnci rozdleni do 4 skupin - 1. skupina neaktivnch osob, ve 2. skupin nedosahovali probandi celkovch doporuen stran fyzick aktivity, splovali vak doporuen 150minut stedn nron fyzick aktivity tdn.pro pijt na workshop pro fit institutu? nae workshopy jsou zameny na konkrtn tmata ivotnho stylu, mezi n pat jdelnky, cvien, motivan techniky, mrnn stresu. respektujeme individuln ivotn poteby, rozdln ivotn rytmus, a proto i cesty k fyzick a psychick pohod jsou pro kadho z ns rzn. nevalme rouby do hlavy (jak se vyjdil jeden z astnk na akce), ale spojujeme do souvislost oven fakta. ukazujeme rzn hly pohledu, ze kterch si vyberete pro vs ten optimln. ekli o ns vborn semin vborn semin. po dlouh dob jsem se bhem tohoto kolen nedval na blackberry. (ladislav kov, citibank, o workshopu a bit of pro fit) pjemn, zajmav setkn pjemn, zajmav setkn umoujc pozastavit se a koncentrovat na dleit otzky. nejvce oceuji fundovanost, pipravenost a uvitelnost vs lektorek. (jana jirasov, hr, procter and gamble, o workshopu 5 krok k fit realit) bezvadn zpracovan bezvadn zpracovan, zbavnou formou, bez zbytench kudrlinek podan tma zlepen ivotnho stylu. motivujc semin s pehledem zkladnch informac a hlavn je lovk veden k zamlen nad vlastnmi cli. (jana o workshopu pro eny na vahch) jsem rda, e jsem se astnila jsem rda, e jsem se semine astnila. dozvdla jsem se spoustu zajmavch a praktickch informac pestoe mi tato tmata nejsou ciz  dobr inspirace a nakopnut. (helena o workshopu srden zleitost) velice m to bavilo velice m to bavilo - cviky, motivace, peky. vyhovovala mi ptelsk atmosfra a vm, e m to jet vc nakopne. (tereza o workshopu 5 krok k fit realit) po naem semini napsala "asn prezentujc odbornice, tmata,co m zajmaj  info do ivota pracujc eny s malm dttem." (daria, zentiva, o workshopu a bit of pro fit ) na naem semini ocenil "velmi pnosn po vech strnkch, velmi oceuji odborn background (vtina nap. poradc ve viv nem medicnsk vzdln a je to poznat)." (michal urban, zentiva, o workshopu a bit fo pro fit) co se na semini lbilo "velmi odborn a vtipn pipraveno a vedeno. ikovn nvody na cvien, zdravou stravu. ochotn odpovdn na dotazy." (karolna svobodov, zentiva, o workshopu a bit of pro fit) pro klademe velk draz na formu prezentace "velmi profesionln prezentace a zajmav a pehledn lenn obsah." (anita, zentiva, o workshopu a bit of pro fit) jak hodnotil n semin "nov a zajmav podan ve sv podstat znm skutenosti." (vclav, zentiva, o workshopu a bit fo pro fit) jak e to bylo? "bylo to vcn. dn pesvdovn o tom co je a nen dobr co velmi oceuji. bylo to pro m srozumiteln. celkov to je velk motivace sama o sob." (jitka snelov, rwe o workshopu den pro fit) k emu workshop nabudil? "zivn, pln informac, cvien. nabuzen k tomu dlat nco sama se sebou  stanoven cle." (martina zhorszk, rwe, o workshopu den pro fit) co se lbilo? co bylo dobr? "lbil se mi projev obou pan doktorek. zajmav bylo aktivn zapojen poslucha. tak bylo dobr ochutnat zdrav jdlo, kter pipravily bhem pestvky." (aranka novkov, rwe, o workshopu den pro fit) jak workshop udroval pozornost? "zajmav, nebyl nudn, udroval pod pozornost dky cvienm a hrm." (astnk, rwe,o workshopu den pro fit) to je nam clem "shrnut a dvn do kontextu vc, kter u jsem kolikrt rzn slyel, ale nevidl jsem souvislosti. podno zbavnou formou." (josef, maek, rwe, o workshopu den pro fit) co bylo na worskhopu nejvtm pnosem? "asn prezentan schopnosti. velk pnos pedevm v praktickch ukzkch, vysvtlovn na pkladech."(nicole wagnerov, rwe, o workshopu den pro fit) co se hod pro ivot? "dn stroh teorie ale mnoho praktickch a hlavn vyuitelnch tip." (vendula blakov, rwe, o workshopu den pro fit) workshop m nakopl "vrtila jsem se po matesk dovolen do zamstnn a bylo toho najednou moc. worskhop mi pomohl urovnat si priority, pochopit, e nen nutn bt ve vem 100% a e pokud budu spokojen j, bude spokojen i moje okol". (petra o workshopu pro eny v pohybu a s nadhledem) smyslupln proit den "je to smyslupln proit den. skvl atmosfra, perfektn organizace, velk motivace! doporuuji vem." (jitka jagersk o workshopu pro eny na vahch) co hned uplatujeme? "kolen bylo asn, praktick. kolegov si sthli krokomry, sdluj si prbn vsledky. stoj kde mohou... j sama sleduji, kde vude je glukzofruktozov sirup a vc pemlm, jak olej pout. informace hned aplikujeme v praxi." noche y madrugada en holgun lluvias localmente intensas se esperan en los municipios mayar, frank pas, sagua de tnamo y moa publicado: jueves 04 agosto 2011 | 04:12:47 pm updated: jueves 21 septiembre 2017 | 09:12:55 pm autor: juventud rebelde digital@juventudrebelde.cu ver ms las provincias orientales deben continuar prestando atencin a las informaciones sobre la evolucin y futura trayectoria de la tormenta tropical emily. autor: instituto de meteorologa publicado: 21/09/2017 | 05:12 pm como resultado de la disminucin de la velocidad de traslacin de la tormenta tropical emily, sus efectos pueden alcanzar al territorio de esta provincia en la prxima noche y madrugada, reporta la ain. presidida por vivian rodrguez, jefa de la defensa civil, en la segunda reunin de hoy del consejo de defensa provincial se alert que lluvias localmente intensas se esperan en los municipios mayar, frank pas, sagua de tnamo y moa. rodrguez, tambin vicepresidenta del rgano de la defensa en la provincia, apunt en la cita que holgun se prepara para afrontar la peor de las variantes, con racionalidad y eficacia en la proteccin de las personas y los recursos de la economa. los 14 consejos municipales de defensa y grupos de trabajo, informaron de las acciones ejecutadas en las ltimas horas, especialmente de las labores encaminadas a preservar los recursos alimentarios almacenados, la situacin de los medios electrgenos y las comunicaciones, entre otros temas. una medida acatada con celeridad fue el retorno de los vacacionistas de las playas y la suspensin de la totalidad de las actividades nuticas, cuando ya se esperan las primeras marejadas en el litoral. el municipio de mayar report que se prepara para evacuar a vecinos de la presa de nipe, que actualmente vierte, mientras frank pas indic la salida preventiva de las 29 familias que residen en canal 5. en estos casos, la prioridad es trasladar a las personas hacia las casas de vecinos y familiares que ofrezcan las condiciones de seguridad adecuadas, aunque otros destinos estn listos para recibir evacuados cuando se decida. manuel paneque, delegado del instituto nacional de recursos hidrulicos en el territorio, seal que las 18 presas y dos derivadoras estn preparadas para asimilar importantes volmenes de lluvias. comparte esta noticia temas holgun ciclones madrugada noche defensa civil meteorologia emily __label__low naar de inhoud springenxooz blogalgemeen gezever en af en toe een dansje maak een backup van je wolk de gmail outage van gisterenmorgenop twitter al ludiek gfail genoemdheeft mij ertoe aangezet nog eens al schrijvend na te denken over wat cloud computing nu eigenlijk zou moeten zijn. the fruits, the pitfalls, the good, the great and the downright evil of web applications. bear with me.google mail, of kortweg gmail, kan zowat gezien worden als een tipping point in de geschiedenis van het web. het was de eerste online mailservice die grotere bijlagen toeliet (nu tot 20 megabyte) en een online opslagcapaciteit van maar liefst 1 gigabyte aanbood (ondertussen al meer dan 7 gb). maar dat was niet de enige belangrijke vernieuwing die zoveel mensen heeft overhaald om van hun hotmailaccount af te stappen. gmail was ook de eerste webmailservice die bovenop de extra opslagcapaciteit conversaties introduceerde; een belangrijke functie die ik alvast niet meer zou kunnen missen. als klap op de vuurpijl was (en is) het hele boeltje virtueel gratis, want het wordt betaald met googles advertentie-inkomsten.na googles maildienst volgden er nog vele andere online applicaties waarmee je je data gratis in de cloud kan opslaan. de cloud is een abstract begrip voor velen. het is misschien nog het makkelijkst te omschrijven als een wolk van digitale data, gevormd door een netwerk van computers en toegankelijk via nderwelke internettoegang ter wereld (behalve in china dan, misschien). wat daarvan het gevolg is, is echt fantastisch: je data zijn altijd en overal beschikbaar, omdat ze in de cloud zijn opgeslagen. op reis in spanje en geen laptop mee, maar toch een belangrijk mailtje nodig? geen probleem: een computer met internettoegang en je kan meteen je mailtje opzoeken. wil je meteen de fotos die je op reis genomen hebt delen met je vrienden en familie? sure thing, gewoon online gaan, de fotos op je flickr- of facebookaccount zetten en ze zijn daar for the world to see.gisteren was er echter eventjes paniek in wolkenland. gmail was voor verschillende mensen niet meer bereikbaar via de webservice (gmail.com of googlemail.com). dat zorgde onder andere op twitter voor nogal wat commotie. afgezien van het feit dat ik een bijna blind vertrouwen heb in de medewerkers en meer specifiek de technische staff van google (komaan: ze doorzoeken het hele internet in gemiddeld 0,15 seconden!) vond ik het toevallig de dag voordien nodig om een backup te nemen van mijn gmail bedrijfsaccounts. ik heb gewoon de pop-functie ingeschakeld en dan thunderbird ingesteld om regelmatig alle e-mail te downloaden. met de juiste filters en instellingen heb ik zelfs helemaal geen last van die one-way backup en kan ik bovendien gemakkelijk mijn mails terugvinden.cloud applicaties zijn leuk. meer zelfs: ik vind ze fantastisch en ik zou niet meer zonder kunnen, maar zoals met alle data is het altijd verstandig om een backup te bewaren. nu, google maakt ongetwijfeld backups op zon manier dat ik zelfs geruster kan zijn dat de hel op mijn hoofd valt, dan dat mijn data onherroepelijk zouden verdwijnen. maar dat neemt niet weg dat een menselijke fout of, god forbid, kwaad opzet er altijd voor kunnen zorgen dat er toch wat misloopt. dat is de reden waarom ik al mijn mails nog eens via pop3 download, waarna ze op geregelde intervallen via time machine automatisch naar mijn backupschijf worden weggeschreven. dat is de reden waarom ik zelf al mijn fotos op mijn harde schijf bewaar. en dat is de reden waarom ik voorlopig met iets meer terughoudendheid naar webapplicaties kijk. is er geen mogelijkheid tot het makkelijk bewaren en synchroniseren van online en offline data? dan gebruik ik de applicatie niet om belangrijke data op te slaan.ps: voorlopig nog in pre-btafase, maar ongemeen interessant om ook offline toegang tot je mail te houden is de nieuwe gmail labs offline feature auteur xy&zgeplaatst op 2009-02-252009-02-25categorien technologie en wetenschaptags backup, cloud, data, gegevens bram hah, ik doe net het omgekeerde! alle dingen op mijn lokale schijf opslaan, en ze periodiek laten synchroniseren met maar bram, heb je dan geen schrik dat andere mensen je gevoelige data kunnen bekijken? nee. bram hah, ik doe net het omgekeerde! alle dingen op mijn lokale schijf opslaan, en ze periodiek laten synchroniseren met maar bram, heb je dan geen schrik dat andere mensen je gevoelige data kunnen bekijken? nee. xavez hmm gebruik je dan ook gmail via pop3? want het is eigenlijk net de interface van gmail die ik zo superieur vind t.o.v. de interface van say apple mail, thunderbird, outlook  xavez hmm gebruik je dan ook gmail via pop3? want het is eigenlijk net de interface van gmail die ik zo superieur vind t.o.v. de interface van say apple mail, thunderbird, outlook  wim leers ik doe het ng anders. of toch een beetje ik gebruik google apps for your domain, de gratis versie natuurlijk. dan gebruik ik gmail via imap, met apples mail.app. aangezien mail.app alles lokaal cachet, heb ik toegang tot alle mails. daarnaast maak ik regelmatig volledige (incrementele) kloons van mijn heel systeem, en dus zijn ook mails gebackupt dan  wim leers ik doe het ng anders. of toch een beetje ik gebruik google apps for your domain, de gratis versie natuurlijk. dan gebruik ik gmail via imap, met apples mail.app. aangezien mail.app alles lokaal cachet, heb ik toegang tot alle mails. daarnaast maak ik regelmatig volledige (incrementele) kloons van mijn heel systeem, en dus zijn ook mails gebackupt dan  xavez welja, toen ik het over de business accounts had, had ik het inderdaad ook op apps for your domain. fantastische tool trouwens ik wist niet dat mail.app de smtp mails ook in de cache bewaarde maar ik ben precies toch iets meer fan van de oplossing die mails ook mooi in een open formaatje opslaat en dat ook bewust doet =].btw: waarom clones van je volledige systeem? en via rsync handmatig dan? geen time machine? :). xavez welja, toen ik het over de business accounts had, had ik het inderdaad ook op apps for your domain. fantastische tool trouwens ik wist niet dat mail.app de smtp mails ook in de cache bewaarde maar ik ben precies toch iets meer fan van de oplossing die mails ook mooi in een open formaatje opslaat en dat ook bewust doet =].btw: waarom clones van je volledige systeem? __label__low skip to main | skip to sidebar awol - the ancient world online issn 2156-2253 thursday, january 11, 2018 newly available in the achemenet digital library newly available in the achemenet digital library jean chardin voyages de monsieur le chevalier chardin en perse et autre lieux de lorient edited by philip stewart (with an introduction) in the course of two long sojourns in persia, jean chardin (1643-1713), a jeweler by trade, parisian and protestant by civil status, and imbued with classic letters, took it on himself to perfect his knowledge of every aspect of the persian world. unlike other well- known frenchmen who travelled in the orient in the same time frame, he took the time to master the persian language. his writings were long the canonical source for anyone seeking information on persia and other muslim countries. there has not been a serious edition of his voyages de chardin en perse et autres lieux de lorient for two centuries. the present enterprise is best understood in the context of the fragmentary and troubled history of the earlier editions... pierre briant (dir.) irrigation et drainage dans lantiquit persika 2, 2001 posted by charles jones at 2:47 pm email thisblogthis!share to twittershare to facebookshare to pinterest no comments: post a comment newer post older post home subscribe to: post comments (atom) digital humanities award translate open philology project digitized books loading... search this blog awol is a project of charles e. jones, tombros librarian for classics and humanities at the pattee library, penn state universityawol began with a series of entries under the heading awol on the ancient world bloggers group blog. i moved it to its own space here beginning in 2009.the primary focus of the project is notice and comment on open access material relating to the ancient world, but i will also include other kinds of networked information as it comes available.the ancient world is conceived here as it is at the institute for the study of the ancient world at new york university, my academic home at the time awol was launched. that is, from the pillars of hercules to the pacific, from the beginnings of human habitation to the late antique / early islamic period.awol is the successor to abzu, a guide to networked open access data relevant to the study and public presentation of the ancient near east and the ancient mediterranean world, founded at the oriental institute, university of chicago in 1994. together they represent the longest sustained effort to map the development of open digital scholarship in any discipline.awol is syndicated to facebook and twitter. pelagios widget blog archive  2018 (400)  april (67)  march (118)  february (104)  january (111) new open access journal: __________________________ preview my book here about me name: tom brown location: so. california, united states i am an american artist and i host a tv art instruction show where i teach studio oil painting and plein air painting in the impressionist style. i also teach other artists how to paint through oil painting workshops and art instruction cds and dvds. my impressionist plein air landscapes, still life compositions, portraits and figure paintings have been represented through prominent galleries for more than 20 years. my paintings are in corporate collections including the city of irvine, sears, standard oil, and coca cola. my work is often seen in leading art publications like southwest art, art & antiques, american art review, american art collector, art calendar and others. i am a former president of the orange art association and past member of the laguna plein air painters association and southern california plein air painters association. on my daily painter blog i offer affordable small original oil paintings to introduce my work to new and ongoing collectors. much of my work these days is done on a private commission basis, and i welcome inquiries. thanks for looking. view my complete profile links my ebay listings my website previous posts full moon by tom brown sunset by tom brown video: fun in the studio with tom brown seascape by tom brown *zipcode done mvn sign in  don't have an account yet? sign up  facebook twitter follow @laweekly instagram follow google plus recommended for you residents of dirty, dilapidated south l.a. house get city help to find new home this year, in california at least, 4/20 is for everyone, pot proponents say pot prices could actually rise after legalization dennis romero expand green currency at the emerald exchange farmers market star foreman/l.a. weekly pot prices could actually rise after legalization dennis romero | november 4, 2016 | 6:49am facebook twitter email print article aa marijuana legalization is good for social justice, its backers say. for too long, drug laws have been used to arrest and incarcerate minorities at much higher rates than whites. plus, pot has been proven to be, as president obama himself put it, less dangerous than alcohol. so instead of creating a black market for criminals, why not tax it and regulate it to benefit the people of california?those arguments sound reasonable  noble, even. but if you are voting purely out of self-interest, you might just vote no on proposition 64, the measure that would legalize recreational marijuana for those 21 and older. why?related storiesas cannabis cultivation grows, california wrestles with marijuana's environmental impactwill marijuana legalization benefit people of color?new study examines medical marijuana's effects on driversfifteen percent taxes on recreational marijuana under the measure will boost the price of weed compared with that guy who sells it out of his apartment. sales tax in some parts of l.a. county is already 10 cents on the dollar. so you're looking at a steep price increase for your organic produce if you were to buy it legally for recreational use. now a study says that even the base wholesale price of weed is likely to go up, at least temporarily, if voters legalize it tuesday.a white paper released this week predicts pot prices will increase after propositions 64's rules open the door to recreational retailers starting in 2018  if the measure passes. "after the gold rush: california, cannabis & the election" by marijuana price data firm cannabis benchmarks looked at what happened after recreational legalization in washington, colorado and oregon to come to its conclusion. washington oregon, in particular, saw rising weed prices in response to legalization, including a $200-per-pound spike, to a price of $1,941, late last year, and a 12 percent spike again this year, according to the paper. the first increase was a result of dispensaries stocking up to meet increased demand; the second was a response to a "supply bottleneck" as regulations forced retailers to buy product that had been tested by accredited laboratories, according to analysis.jonathan rubin, ceo of cannabis benchmarks, explained that the following factors could increase postlegalization prices in california:compliance: proposition 64 will mandate licenses for growers and sellers, and it will regulate packaging and labeling. this stuff costs money.stocking up: dispensaries will engage in "advanced buying to make sure their shelves are stocked" on jan. 1, 2018, when, if 64 passes, anyone with a heartbeat and an id proving they're 21 or older can walk into a dispensary and buy pot, rubin said. demand: because almost anyone will be able to buy weed, demand is expected to multiply. higher demand can mean higher prices.testing: mandatory product testing not only slows down the supply line and adds costs for producers but it also means that noncompliant product can be held and even destroyed, rubin explained. less supply can mean higher prices. if you like this story, consider signing up for our email newsletters. show me how x newsletters all-access pass to the top stories, events and offers around town. no thanks sign up x success! you have successfully signed up for your selected newsletter(s) - please keep an eye on your mailbox, we're movin' in! these are all factors that contributed to price increases in other states that have legalized recreational marijuana. however, rubin acknowledges that california is a different beast. he says experts generally agree that about 80 percent of america's weed comes from the golden state. outdoor growers here have massive capacity, and that might help to mitigate some price fluctuation.but rubin says he believes consumers will still see higher-priced pot. "in almost every commodity market, the end user is the one costs get passed on to," he says.the increases could be temporary, part of a "boom-bust cycle" where entrepreneurs rush into an emerging market and create so much product and so much competition that prices soon level off. "when prices are high it attracts more players, you have more competition, more supply, and price goes down," rubin says."longer-term, prices will stabilize as market forces reach equilibrium," he says. "this will afford existing cultivators and early entrants the opportunity to optimize their operations and secure their competitive position." dennis romero is an l.a. weekly staff writer. he formerly worked at the philadelphia inquirer and the los angeles times, where he participated in pulitzer prize-winning coverage of the l.a. riots. his work has appeared in rolling stone online, the guardian and, as a young stringer, the new york times. contact: dennis romero follow: twitter: @dennisjromero popular stories the search for spirituality and wellness is driving new image... who knew? six famous potheads in history skid row's walk the talk parade celebrates the community and... this year, in california at least, 4/20 is for everyone, pot... 2018 la weekly, lp. all rights reserved. newsletters all-access pass to the top stories, events and offers around town. top stories send: sign up > remind me later > no thanks > privacy policy newsletters all-access pass to top stories, events and offers around town. sign up > no thanks! remind me later >

report details product title the 2016-2021 outlook for fresh fruit juices and nectars in japan captcha code * refresh copy the code given in the image on the left side. request sample abstract content related reports this econometric study covers the latent demand outlook for fresh fruit juices and nectars across the prefectures and cities of japan. latent demand (in millions of u.s. dollars), or potential industry earnings (p.i.e.) estimates are given across some 1,000 cities in japan. this statistical approach can prove very useful to distribution and/or sales force strategies. using econometric models which project fundamental economic dynamics within each prefecture and city, latent demand estimates are created for fresh fruit juices and nectars. this report does not discuss the specific players in the market serving the latent demand, nor specific details at the product level. the study also does not consider short-term cyclicalities that might affect realized sales. the study, therefore, is strategic in nature, taking an aggregate and long-run view, irrespective of the players or products involved. this study does not report actual sales data (which are simply unavailable, in a comparable or consistent manner in virtually all of the cities in japan). this study gives, however, my estimates for the latent demand, or the p.i.e., for fresh fruit juices and nectars in japan. it also shows how the p.i.e. is divided and concentrated across the cities and regional markets of japan. table of contents: 1 introduction 101.1 overview 101.2 what is latent demand and the p.i.e.? 101.3 the methodology 111.3.1 step 1. product definition and data collection 121.3.2 step 2. filtering and smoothing 131.3.3 step 3. filling in missing values 131.3.4 step 4. varying parameter, non-linear estimation 141.3.5 step 5. fixed-parameter linear estimation 141.3.6 step 6. aggregation and benchmarking 141.4 frequently asked questions (faq) 151.4.1 category definition 151.4.2 units 151.4.3 methodology 162 summary of findings 182.1 the latent demand in japan 182.2 top 100 cities sorted by rank 213 aichi 243.1 latent demand by year - aichi 243.2 cities sorted by rank __label__low neaststyle area rugs & shag rugs you'll love home / shag rugs / top 53 superlative lime green shag area rug inventivenesstop 53 superlative lime green shag area rug inventiveness coletta jung shag rugs march 26, 2018 23:03:55these are available in a variety of materials ranging from acrylic nylon cotton rayon wool yarn blends and a cotton base to keep it from slipping or a same sized rug pad can be used to keep your rug clean and anti slip. with changing lifestyles and fast paced life everyone looks for low maintenance carpets and rugs so shag rugs win hands down. easy to clean and can be added in any decor makes then a very viable option when looking to redecorate any room. available in innovative colors sizes and designs they fit into any decor and size of the room.finally shag rugs have branched out into a new material: leather. at first the thought of leather rugs can be startling but theyre ideal for a bachelors masculine abode or for an executive suite. made of natural leather suede or a combination of the two these shags boast thick ruffled strands that result in a sturdy dense surface that holds its shape against all comers. most leather shags come in the same dark colors typical of leather furniture: black brown tan chocolate and sometimes white or red.popular post in shag rugsaffordable shag rugsblack and white shag rugscolorful shag rugsblack round shag rugshag rugs first came to popularity in the late 1960s and early 1970s as an expression of the pop art movement. they began to lose their appeal as the movement waned and for a while shag rugs simply fell out of favor. however new manufacturing techniques to say nothing of a wide range of styles and colors have lifted shags from the scrap heap of decorating history.most viewed gallery in shag rugsbamboo shag rugbello shag rugblue and brown shag rug6 x 9 shag rugthe shag rug really is popular right now and that is probably because of its diversity. a rug that can be used in just about any room to add style and texture is great! while shag carpeting will likely not be seen as it was in the past shag rugs are very popular for the time being.typically shag rugs can be made from cotton acrylic polypropylene and nylon and are available in a host of colors to suit every taste and need. these rugs all have a similarity in appearance in the sense that their texture and appearance consist of strands of knotted material. these are either short or long in appearance or a combination of both.shag rugs come in a multitude of colors and the pile range depth is from one inch to about two and a half inch giving that luxurious softness and lush style. usually rugs are tufted or woven in loops and then sheared to get the short fibers but shag rugs are left without shearing the length and that gives them that deep piled lush soft feel. if you are looking for an extra soft warm shag rug go in for rugs that have a high pile of over 2 inches. the shorter pile gives less warmth and softness. 64 out of 100 based on 891 user ratings 1 star 2 star 3 star 4 star 5 star tagslarge area rugs cheapbrown shag rugturquoise area ruggrey area rugshag ruglime green shag rugsoft area rugsteal rugorange shag rugshag pile rugplush rugswhite shag area rugarea carpetscheap shag rugslarge white ruggallery of top 53 superlative lime green shag area rug inventiveness have something to say on top guideline because you might want a tighter or looser fit. when in doubt or you fall in between sizes we suggest ordering a size up. if you are unsure of your measurements, click here to review tips to jacket adult sport lace jersey hooded pullover by j. america product details loading... this may take a few seconds. what is sewn on twill? sewn on twill, or tackle twill, is a technique in which pieces of fabric, usually a poly/cotton twill, are cut out and then sewn or embroidered onto your garment providing a more professional look. what is embroidery applique? embroidery applique is a non-woven, super soft material that looks great on sweatshirts and activewear. it provides a classic look that is durable and washable and is ideal for creating vintage designs. a note about embroidered monograms: a monogram is a motif made by overlapping or combining two or more letters. monograms are often made by combining the initials of an individual or a company, used as recognizable symbols. classic three letter monogram layout for an individual is with the last name initial larger and in the center of the monogram (first name - last name - middle name) john q. smith : jsq. a note about screenprinting: buy in quantities of 24-pieces or more and take advantage of low pricing to screenprint one or two color graphics. low prices, no setup fees. need help? call our __label__low eduvidya.com home colleges courses schools exams universities distance education study abroad queries blogs search homecolleges in indiaindian institute of forest management bhopal indian institute of forest management bhopal established in : 1982affiliated to : ministry of environment and forestswebsite : www.iifm.ac.inaddress : po box 357, nehru nagar, bhopal, madhya pradesh, india contact no : 0755-2775716, 2773799 email: director@iifm.ac.in (3 out of 5 based on 2 ratings) rate this college need admission help? about admissions facilities courses exams placements address map photos videos compare colleges indian institute of forest management is an autonomous institution in bhopal that strives to develop and equip students with essential skills in the field of forest management. it was set up in the year 1982 by ministry of environment and forests, government of india. being one of the premier forest management institutes, it offers two years, full time post graduate diploma in forest management that is equivalent to mba. doctorate-level courses, management development programmes and summer internship are also conducted by the college. nirf ranking 2018 - management - 41 admissions: admission to the fully residential two year pgdfm is open to graduates from any discipline provided he/she fulfils the eligibility criteria and qualifies through the selection proces step-1: :common admission test (cat) all applicants desirous of seeking admission in pgdfm at iifm have to appear for common admission test (cat) conducted by indian institute of management (iims), by responding to their notification published in leading national dailies. iifm will use the cat score for short-listing the candidates for two year full time post graduate programme. iims have no role either in the selection process or in the conduct of the programme. step-2: iifm application form: in addition to cat, the candidate should also fill-up a separate form for admission to pgdfm, which is available from iifm bhopal. the cost of iifm application form is rs. 900/- (450/- for sc/ st) payable at bhopal. this can be obtained either personally or by post. the application form can also be downloaded from our website and in that case, the completed application form should accompany the demand draft of the specified amount drawn in favour of director, indian institute of forest management payable at bhopal. step-3: group discussion/interview: candidates short listed on the basis of cat score, will be called for group discussion and interview during february/march 2013 based on the choice of candidates, as mentioned in the application form. reservation :- 15%, 7.5%, 27% and 3% of the seats are reserved for candidates belonging to the sc, st, non-creamy-obc and da (also referred to as persons with disability) (pwd) respectively, provided they meet the minimum selection criteria as specified by iifm. the mandatory disclosure as per aicte guidelines relating to admission procedure is hosted on our website. facilities: indian institute of forest management is located on a picturesque hill in southwestern part of the bhopal city. the campus is famous for its rich flora and fauna with views of various small sized wild animals and birds. the architect of the institutes building is famous for its historical design. the institute has a good faculty student ratio and the very best infrastructure in terms of computing and library facilities. it is a fully residential course with 93 seats. courses: indian institute of forest management bhopal courses offered exams accepted: cat placements: address: po box 357, nehru nagar, bhopal, madhya pradesh, india contact no : 0755-2775716, 2773799 email: director@iifm.ac.in photos indian institute of forest management bhopal entrance videos indian institute of forest management bhopal group dance map: review: need education loan? other colleges in same city nri institute of pharmacy bansal diploma pharmacy college ihm bhopal maulana azad national institute of technology laxmi narayan college of pharmacy comments reviews questions name: email: mobile: comments: name: civil engineering the drainage and infrastructure aspects of a project are fundamental to its successful delivery. we provide bespoke services to suit every site regardless of the nature of the proposed development. we operate across a broad range of sectors from residential to education, bluelight to industrial, whatever the type of client we can provide a full cradle to grave service, or tailor our input to suit a specific design stage or service element. we always seek to provide sustainable solutions that add value to the clients brief both during construction and throughout the whole life cycle. highway services include: s.278 agreements for public highway works s.38 agreements for highway adoption external works and construction specifications site preparation (enabling and earthworks) drainage services include: initial drainage strategy sustainable drainage systems (suds) flood risk assessments flood mitigation measures adoptable surface, foul and highways drainage all private drainage requirements structural engineering structural engineering lies at the heart of all good building projects and it is our engineering skill that helps to deliver successful projects. as a result, ingleton woods engineers are an integral part of the project delivery team. we are experienced in all the main sectors: retail, residential, industrial, health, commercial, scientific research, education; as well as historic buildings and conservation projects. our structural services include: structural inspections (building defects and repairs) foundation design basement and retaining wall design structural masonry, timber, reinforced concrete and steel design timber frame and cold formed metal frame design engineering excellence is not just about design, it is also about having a good understanding of the construction process and modern procurement methods. when coupled with a sound knowledge of how buildings fit together real value can be added to any scheme. whether it is traditional methods, pre-assembled elements, modular design or sustainable forms of construction; our team of engineers have the knowledge and experience to deliver. please see our civil and structural engineering pages for further details. related linksour servicescivil engineeringstructural engineeringour projectsst georges church of england school elm street st helena school new __label__low testimonianze - bomboniere solidali vai ai contenuti menu principale: home il progetto testimonianze chi siamo contatti faq . se desideri anche tu dare la tua testimonianza compila l'apposito form. saremo felici di pubblicarla. "ho comprato le bomboniere solidali di humana per il mio matrimonio. mio marito, carlo, allinizio non era molto daccordo. lui  tradizionalista (e mia suocera ancor di pi!), voleva andare in un negozio (magari anche pi di uno), vederne di diversi modelli e di diversi prezzi. quindi quando gli ho proposto di avere delle bomboniere solidali vi potete immaginare la sua espressione! poi si  convinto a visitare il sito di humana e quando ha visitato la pagina del progetto che sostenevamo con le nostre bomboniere non ho pi potuto fermarlo! vedere i visi dei bambini, sapere che nel nostro giorno pi bello avremmo potuto aiutare anche tutti quei faccini ha fatto s che carlo prendesse la decisione pi forte in tutta lorganizzazione del nostro matrimonio: sfidare sua mamma e le cose "fatte alla vecchia maniera"! posso solo dire grazie a humana, le bomboniere sono state apprezzate da tutti e ammetto che oltre allimpegno di solidariet che esprimevano erano veramente bellissime, tutte fatte a mano e recapitate in tempo."giovanna. "ho sempre voluto fare la volontaria, ma prima lo studio, poi il lavoro, il matrimonio e i figli me lo hanno sempre impedito. quando dovevamo decidere cosa fare per la comunione di matteo non ci sono stati dubbi: scegliamo un agriturismo, pochi invitati e soprattutto facciamo le bomboniere solidali! sono capitata nel sito di humana e il mio matteo ha scelto dei simpaticissimi portachiavi con gufi e uccellini ed io mi sono innamorata di un progetto cos semplice ed efficace che d cibo, istruzione e assistenza sanitaria a bambini orfani. adesso guardo lunico portachiavi che c rimasto a casa, matteo lha voluto in cameretta, a volte la sera mentre gli leggo la storia della buona notte lo guarda e mi dice: sai mamma, forse uno dei bimbi che abbiamo aiutato comprando il gufetto sta anche lui ascoltando una storia..ed io capisco che ho proprio fatto la scelta giusta.maria ho scelto le bomboniere solidali di humana perch sono un affezionato, un volontario dellassociazione da anni. quando ho deciso di fare il grande passo con lucia non potevamo che scegliere di fare le bomboniere con humana, un dono che avesse un valore pi nobile. ancora una volta grazie a humana di aver capito le esigenze di chi ha di fronte, abbiamo proprio trovato le bomboniere che facevano per noi!gianluca. un veloce grazie a humana per le sue bellissime bomboniere! alla comunione di mia figlia con i segnalibri di legno abbiamo fatto un figurone!patrizia. io non ho ordinato le bomboniere solidali di humana, le ho ricevute. al matrimonio di luca, il mio pi caro amico, ho ricevuto questa bella scatolina e dentro scopro che non ci sono solo i confettic laiuto ai bambini orfani e svantaggiati in zambia. allora, io e la mia fidanzata abbiamo deciso di fare un regalo speciale agli sposi post-matrimonio, visto che eravamo i due testimoni dello sposo: abbiamo attivato per loro un sostegno a distanza per un bambino in zambia. luca e paola sono rimasti contentissimi, hanno avuto la prova che le loro bomboniere solidali erano state apprezzate e capite e adesso hanno un legame speciale con un bambino lontano.cristiano. i gufetti sono bellissimi, la mamma mi ha detto che siete stati voi a farli e che cos abbiamo aiutato dei bambini poveri! grazie per averceli mandati. ma non si pu scrivere a quei bambini? mi piacerebbe molto, ma se voi gli telefonate vi prego, ditegli che serena li saluta!serena 9 anni. grazie humana per le bellissime bomboniere! sono stata felicissima di avervi scelto per ricordare la mia laurea e grazie ancora per avermi dato la possibilit di essere daiuto ai bambini in africadonatella. il tuo nome* e-mail* ripeti e-mail* scrivi la tua testimonianza* se vuoi inserire una fotografia (formato jpg - max 300 kb) liberatoria per la pubblicazione*acconsento alla pubblicazione del mio nome, della testimonianza e della fotografia (se allegata) sul sito www.humanaitalia.itaccetto home | il progetto | testimonianze | chi siamo | contatti | faq | . | mappa generale del sito torna ai contenuti | torna al menu per poter utilizzare questo sito  necessario attivare javascript.

tollywood movie reviews agnyaathavaasi movie review, rating, story, cast and crew agnyaathavaasi movie review, rating, story, cast and crew twitter facebook google + pinterest rating: (3/5) director: trivikram srinivas cast: pawan kalyan, keerthy suresh, anu emmanuel banner: haarika & hassine creations producer: s. radha krishna music: anirudh ravichander release dt : jan, 10 2018 story agnyaathavaasi is all about abhishikth bhargav (pawan kalyan) who leads a secret life because of the rivals of his father govind bhargav (boman irani). the day arrives after his father gets brutally by his opponents after which the whole world arrives for the successor of ab group which govind owns. it is during this time, govinds wife indrani (kusbhoo) sets a deadline of abhis arrival. the rest of agnyaathavaasi is all about the arrival of the prince in his style and how he treats his rivals. watch agnyaathavaasi to know about the complete story. analysis the first half of agnyaathavaasi looks pale and poorly written. one expects a strong set of episodes from trivikram along with some entertaining episodes that went missing completely in agnyaathavaasi. the songs have been placed well and they have been shot well across some beautiful locales. the action episodes have been shot well and the interval episodes make a massive impact. on the whole, the first half of agnyaathavaasi looks decent. the second half of the film manages to stand tall for twenty minutes but it dips down again as the film proceeds. the songs look decent and the entertainment keeps the audience engaging. though the major plot has been left deviated, the focus stands completely on pawan kalyan. the rest of the episodes how abhi retains the business empire have been loosely executed and the climax has been quite simple. on the whole, the second half of agnyaathavaasi too has been just ok and misses the mark of trivikram badly. performance pawan kalyan takes the lead as abhi and he tops the show with his flawless performance. he tried his best to save agnyaathavaasi and his screen presence has been exceptional. the actor has been outstanding in the emotional episodes. boman irani has been subtle and he steals the show with his performance in the crisp role. kusbhoo has been extremely emotional and she has been quite expressive throughout. keerthy suresh looks fit and has been decent. anu emmanuel looks extremely glamorous and is a treat for frontbenchers. all the other actors delivered out their best for the film. the story of agnyaathavaasi has been inspired from the french film largo winch. the screenplay and the dialogues lack the mark of trivikram which is a huge disappointment for the film. the music and the background score have been soothing and apt for the film. the cinematography is the major asset for the film along with the lavish production values that make the film look rich in each and every frame. agnyaathavaasi should be appreciated for the technical aspects and trivikrams work for agnyaathavaasi will be badly criticised. final word pawan kalyan and the lead actors steal the show with their impeccable performances throughout but trivikrams poor writing skills make agnyaathavaasi an average watch. stills from this movie videos & trailers twitter facebook google + pinterest tagged under : agnyaathavaasi movie review agnyaathavaasi rating you have four powertrains to choos... choosing the 2018 ford focus you want is no easy task. all models are sleek, sporty and designed to attract attention. if theres one word that sums up the focus driving experience, it would be fun. for starters, you have four powertrains to choose from. and speaking of curves, standard torque vectoring control and electric power-assisted steering let you get the most out of them. focus has standard torque vectoring control, which is designed to help the front wheels grip and steer better while cornering or driving in slippery conditions. the focus interior is as attractive as it is comfortable. fine quality is evident in details such as available alloy trim and the french seams of the available leather-trimmed seating. cloth bucket seats with
